               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsān za-qǝddus Yoḥannǝs walda Zäbdewos baʾǝnta ʿǝbäya wa-kǝbra
                     la-Māryām “Homily by John the Son of Zebedee on the Greatness and Glory of
                     Mary” (fols. 2ra-18rb) (the work known as Rāʾǝya Māryām, or Apocalypse of Mary,
                     M. CHAINE, Apocrypha de B. Maria virgine, Romae - Parisiis - Lipsiae 1909 (CSCO
                     39, 40, SAe7, text pp. 53-80; cp. EAE III, 882-883).</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>The incipit of the text is as follows: [<locus target="#2ra">2ra</locus>]
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አምላክ፡ ፩፡ አምላክ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ኦእግዚእየ፡ ወአምላኪየ። ትስአል፡ ሊተ፡
                        ድርሳነ፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ወብፁዕ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወልደ፡ ዘብዴዎስ፡ በእንተ፡ ዕበያ፡ ወክብራ፡ ለማርያም፡ ቅድስት፡ ድንግል፤
                        …</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
